parameters.name: input_dataset
parameters.description: Input dataset from huggingface.co/datasets (e.g. 'dair-ai/emotion')

parameters.name: dataset_type
parameters.description: Dataset type from huggingface.co/datasets (currently could be either 'text' or 'image')

parameters.name: dataset_config
parameters.description: Dataset configuration (e.g. 'default'). This is indicated in from huggingface.co/datasets when you click in the 'Use in the Datasets library' button as a second argument of the load_dataset function.

parameters.description: The number of output channels from the convolution
